    "title": "TVS Motor is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "TVS Motor is actively seeking a talented and motivated Quality Control Engineer to join our dynamic team in Jaipur. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout TVS Motor:\nTVS Motor is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Implement 5S, Kaizen, and Six Sigma practices on the shop floor\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with TVS Motor!",
